AFTER 'BRUN QUICK KEYS'; THEFOLLOWING SHORTCUTS BECOME ACTIVE:OPEN-APPLE-H - CLEARS THE TEXTSCREENOPEN-APPLE-G - SETS THE HI-RESSCREENOPEN-APPLE-T - SETS THE TEXT DISPLAYOPEN-APPLE-S - POKE 33;33OPEN-APPLE-B - RETURN TO NORMAL TEXTSCREEN DIMENSIONSOPEN-APPLE-M - ENTER THE MONITOROPEN-APPLE-R - RETURN TO BASICOPEN-APPLE-C - CATALOG THE DISKOPEN-APPLE-P - SURPRISEDELETE - DELETES THE CHARACTERBEFORE THE CURSOR AND MOVES IT BACK